{"tid":811447,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【強國人民】為救同胞闖公路 3村民被撞飛1死2傷","createTime":"2018-09-08T20:43:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-08T20:54:51.000Z","uid":179810,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d9262f082501feb002a995dc53022868095097f0","tid":811447,"uid":179810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T20:43:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180908/58655099\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180908%2F58655099&d=EeaBWpaP66fxj6hkiHlU7f6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=bdcaa4a1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180908%2F58655099&h=7caaef18\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180908/58655099</a><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180907/large/1536326443_9b96.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180907%2Flarge%2F1536326443_9b96.jpg&h=1efa6e61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n今次真是貪心貪出禍，連性命都賠上。重慶合川境內公路發生的一場車禍短片，近日在微信朋友圈被廣泛轉發，有3個當地村民因為想撿走高速公路上的一頭生豬，最終被車撞擊，釀成1死2傷的慘劇。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n有關短片於本周三（5日）開始於朋友圈被大量轉發，事源一輛運送豬隻的貨車日前經過合川大橋時，跌出一頭生豬，被3個當地村民見到後，便走入高速公路，想將生豬抬走，但期間不幸被一架白色私家車撞倒，導致其中一名村民當場死亡，另外2個村民則受傷，而事件中的主角生豬，亦被當場撞死。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n網民講乜：<br />\r\n<br />\r\n平仔無極：為了一頭豬把命搭上，值得嗎？<br />\r\n<br />\r\n暗子之血：比豬還蠢。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n靜悅清未：還好，死也有個伴。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n悠然在人間：要豬不要命。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n生威足球俱樂部：人家也許是想抬開，怕影響交通呢。<br />\r\n<br />\r\njoemo：貪小便宜吃大虧。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n老牛KO：無知的代價。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n澎湃新聞網/新浪微博"},{"pid":"7322cdb73c6b6b0c5aa83051041ab73ced24bba6","tid":811447,"uid":23189,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T20:45:27.000Z","msg":"2死2傷喎"},{"pid":"ddfdc749c059a16c41270dbb1554b32c19b51c21","tid":811447,"uid":35557,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T20:50:49.000Z","msg":"幫隻豬打格<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"890b80ee00392851a5047dd9c779f7f734fb5769","tid":811447,"uid":35930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T20:54:51.000Z","msg":"幫隻豬墊屍底，都算死得有價值<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}